  <num>16-2822</num>
  <heading>Mediator costs.</heading>
  <text>Unless otherwise agreed by the parties, the costs of mediation, if any, shall be equally shared by the parties.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation doc="D.C. Law 16-263" type="History">Mar. 14, 2007, D.C. Law 16-263, § 302, 54 DCR 807</annotation>
